<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Ash</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>灰</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>We'll still be friends, she said.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>我们还会是朋友，她说。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Grand, he answered, and then he was walking down a street by himself, before he fully understood what had happened. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——很好，他回答道，然后在他完全弄明白发生了什么事之前，他一个人沿着街道走去。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He knew the street, although not very well. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他认识这条街，尽管不怎么熟悉。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He wasn't sure why he was there, why they'd gone over to this part of the city. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他不确定他为什么在那里，他们为什么跑到了城市的这一地区。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>His wife had just told him she was leaving him. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他妻子刚刚告诉他她要离开他。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Or he was leaving her. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>或者他要离开她。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>One or the other.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>不是这个就是那个。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>And they'd still be friends.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>而且他们还会是朋友。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Grand.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>很好。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He made it home. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他回家了。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He got the Dart, figured out how to get a one-way ticket out of the vending machine at the station. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他到了都柏林快铁站，弄清楚怎么从车站里的自动售票机上买到一张单程票。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He'd left the car for his wife. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他把车留给了他妻子。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>She wasn't there when he got in. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他上车时她不在那里。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He paid the babysitter.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他给临时来照看孩子的保姆付了钱。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Later, Ciara came home. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>稍后，西亚拉（Ciara）会家了。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>And she was all over him. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>并且她整个人趴在他身上。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>She climbed onto him and cried as she came.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>她爬到他身上，而且她来时哭了。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- I'm so, so sorry.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——真的很对不起。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>And that was that, he thought, if it had ever been anything in the first place. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>那确实如此，他想，如果起初曾经有过什么事的话。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He didn't want to ask her if she'd actually told him that she was leaving him. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他不想问她她是不是真的跟他说过她要离开他。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He knew she had. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他知道她说过。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>It didn't matter.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>这没关系。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- You'll be fine, she said, after she'd kissed his stomach and lay tucked in beside him. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——你会没事的，在吻了吻他的肚子并钻进被窝躺在他旁边之后她说。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He'd passed a test, or something. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他通过了一项考试，或什么东西。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He was delighted. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他很高兴。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>She was gone in the morning.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>到早上她已经走了。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He went to work. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他去上班。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>The house was empty when he got home after collecting the girls. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他接了女儿回到家时，家里没人。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He thought, This is it, this is me. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他想，就是这样的，这就是我。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>I live alone. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>我一个人生活。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>With the kids. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>和孩子们一起。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>She'd taken nothing. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>她什么也没拿走。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>The bedroom was exactly the same. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>卧室完全是老样子。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Her book was still beside the bed.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>她的书还在床旁边。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>She came in very late. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>她回来得很晚。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He wasn't sure- he didn't know- if she'd changed her mind or if she'd just come home later than usual. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他不确定——他不知道——她是改主意了还是她只是比平时回来得晚。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>She was drunk- he didn't ask. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>她喝醉了——他没问。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>She rode him again, said nothing about being sorry this time. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>她又一次与他XXOO，这次没有说什么对不起。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>She didn't cry.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>她没哭。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Then she was gone again.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>然后她又走了。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He put Erica and Wanda to bed again the next night, made them brush their teeth, read a story to them. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>第二天晚上他再一次安顿埃里卡（Erica）和旺达（Wanda）上床睡觉，叫她们刷牙，给她们读故事。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>"Kipper's Toybox," twice.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>“奇普的玩具箱”，两次。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Where's Mammy?</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——妈咪在哪里？</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Work.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——工作。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Poor Mammy.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——可怜的妈咪。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Yeah.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——是啊。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He turned off their light and made sure their bedroom door was open exactly as wide as they wanted it.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他关掉她们的灯，确保她们卧室的门打开的幅度恰是她们想要的。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- More.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——再多一点。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- No, stop.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——不，停下。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- More.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——再多一点。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He went downstairs. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他下楼。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Ciara didn't come in. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>西亚拉没回来。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He put the mobile phone beside him, on the arm of the chair. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他把手机放在他旁边，放在椅子的扶手上。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He watched telly. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他看电视。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He slept. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他睡了。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>She didn't phone. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>她没打来电话。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He went up to the bed. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他上楼去睡。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He turned off the light.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他关掉灯。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He woke up. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他醒了。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>She wasn't there. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>她不在。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Three in the morning. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>凌晨三点。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>And she wasn't downstairs. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>她也不在楼下。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He went back up to the bed but he didn't sleep. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他回楼上上床但他没睡。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He went down to the kitchen again. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他又下楼去厨房。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He accepted it as he put the coffee on the hob: She's left me.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他把咖啡放在铁架上时他接受了：她离开我了。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>You think she has? said his brother, Mick.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>你认为她已经走了？他兄弟米克（Mick）说。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Yeah.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——是的。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- You think? said Mick.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——你认为？米克说。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>They were in the kitchen.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他们在厨房里。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Yeah.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——是的。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Well, like. Did she actually tell you she was leaving?</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——哦，那个，她真的告诉你她要离开？</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Yeah, he said. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——是的，他说。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>I think so.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>我想是这样的。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- You fuckin' think so? </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——你他妈的想是这样的？</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Jesus, Kev, you can fuckin' do better than that.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>天啊，凯文，你他妈的能做得更好点。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- She told me.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——她跟我说的。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Grand. And what happened then?</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——很好，然后又发生了什么事？</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- She rode the arse off me.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——她和我XXOO。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Strange, said Mick. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——奇怪，米克说。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>But it makes sense, too. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>但也有意义。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>The long goodbye. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>长长的告别。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>The ride of the guilty. You've heard of it.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>内疚的XXOO，你听说过的。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- No.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——没有。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- It's brilliant, said Mick. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——精彩，米克说。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>I recommend it. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>赞一个。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>What happened then?</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>然后发生了什么事？</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- I think she went to work.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——我想她去上班了。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Is she riding anyone else?</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——她在和其他什么人XXOO吗？</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>The question shocked him. Although it shouldn't have. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>这个问题使他震惊，尽管本不该。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>It annoyed him, the invasion. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>这使他气恼，那个入侵。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>And frightened him.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>并使他害怕。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- I don't think so, he said.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——我想不是这样的，他说。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Think again.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——再想想。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
