</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Well, look it, man, said Mick. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——哦，你看，哥们，米克说。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Just to remind you. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>只是提醒你。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>I live in a poxy one-room flat because I had a short, meaningless fling with my son's religion-and-civics teacher, who gave him a note to give to me and he- and I love my son, I blame only myself- he gave the note to his mother instead. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>我住在一间廉价的一居室公寓里是因为我和我儿子的宗教-和-公民学老师有一段短短的毫无意义的风流事，她给他一封短信要交给我但他——我爱我儿子，我只怪我自己——他却把这封短信给了他妈妈。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Who read it, and it said- </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>她看了信，信上说——</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- I know.</seg>
</tuv>
