</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Ten words that shook the fuckin' world.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——震动了他妈的世界的十个字。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>They were enjoying themselves.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他们很快活。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- And you want to know what I'd do if I was in your position?</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——想知道如果我在你这种情况下我会怎么做吗？</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
