</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He went to his room- their room- and started throwing the shoes back into the wardrobe.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他去他的房间——他们的房间——开始把鞋子扔回衣橱里。</seg>
