</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——对不起。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He got down on his knees and put the shoes and boots away, quietly. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他跪下来，把鞋和靴子放好，静静地。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
