<seg>He piled them. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他把它们堆起来。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>The wardrobe door swung slowly toward him, and with it the full-length mirror. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>衣橱门慢慢向他转过来，和它一起的是那面全身的镜子。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He looked, and saw nothing. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他看看，什么也没看到。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He wasn't there. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他不在那里。</seg>
