<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>她的语音信箱没了。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>It was the automated voice, the Vodafone woman, telling him to leave a message. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>是自动化的声音，沃达丰（Vodafone）女人，叫他留言。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>He had nothing ready and he couldn't think of anything he wanted to say out loud- The kids miss you; I miss you; Where the fuck are you, you stupid mad bitch of a cunt?- so he said nothing.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他没准备什么，他也想不出他要大声说出什么——孩子想你；我想你；你他妈在哪儿，你这又蠢又疯的混蛋婊子？——所以他什么也没说。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
