<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Mick texted.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>米克发来短信。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Jcksns, snday.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>杰克逊，周日。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>Jackson's was a pub near Mick's place. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>杰克逊是一家离米克住所不远的酒馆。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>It was an ordinary pub six nights a week but on Sundays, according to Mick, it changed. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>一个星期里有六晚它是一家普通酒馆，但是在星期天，照米克所说，它就变了。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>It filled up with men- n wmn- of a certain age, who were no longer married or had never been married.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>里面挤满了男人——没女人——有一定岁数的，他们离婚了或从没结过婚。</seg>
