<seg>They were laughing.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>他们大笑。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- Works for me, said Mick. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——对我有用，米克说。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>No one goes home empty-handed.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>没人空手回家。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
