<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>- I'm telling yeh, man, said Kevin. </seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>——我跟你说，哥们，凯文说。</seg>
</tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
<tuv xml:lang="EN-US">
<seg>I went home the last time with fifty-seven-year-old twins.</seg>
</tuv>
<tuv xml:lang="ZH-CN">
<seg>我上次带一对五十七岁的双胞胎回家。</seg>
